My game uses if/then logic to control the win and lose conditions. 
If the player collects all of the pages, the game loads the Win Screen. 
If the player’s health reaches zero, the game loads the Game Over Screen. 
The game starts at the Main Menu, then moves to a Loading Scene, which automatically transitions into Level 1 after a short delay. 
The end screens display clear win or lose messages and include buttons to restart the game or exit.
